                    <h4 class="modal-title">Level 3 Consent Question</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>
                        If a candidate's name appears on merit, he must give consent in the first round to go in the next round.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If a candidate's name did not appear in the first round, he should wait for the next round. Maybe his name will appear in next round (if any).
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If a candidate's name appears in all the 3 disciplines namely FCPS, MS & MD, he will be able to give consent for only 1 seat and in the second round he will be able to give consent for only related seats.<br />
                        (If consent is given for FCPS then will not be able to give consent for MD and MS)<br />
                        (If consent is given for MD then will not be able to give consent for FCPS and MS)<br />
                        (If consent is given for MS then will not be able to give consent for FCPS and MD)
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If a candidate's name appears in two disciplines, he will be able to give consent for only one seat and in the next round he will be able to give consent for the relevant seats (if his name appears on merit and if he applied) as well as for the program where has not been selected currently.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If a candidate's name appears in one discipline, he will be able to give consent only for that seat and in the second round he will be able to give consent for the rest of the disciplines (if his name appears on merit and if he applied).
                    </p>
                    <br />
                    <h2> Please Note</h2>
                    <p>
                        In every consequent list if candidate name appears in any program, need to give consent against that program for further process in coming round
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If you failed to give consent, you will not consider to next round whether you are on same preference or top on preference.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If you give consent to other program even, you are at same preference in previous round you will not consider to that specific program
                    </p>
                    <p>
                       In every list if your name appear in any program you have to give consent otherwise your name will be excluded for induction process
                    </p>
                   
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
